ActCanada Revenue Agency Act
PrecisAppointment of SUSAN L. GREEN of Edmonton, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Management of the Canada Revenue Agency, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Myles Bourke, whose term has expired.
